  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Share Action-Fair Finance Guide UK</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project will contribute to the creation of a Fair Finance Guide coalition in the UK, through the development of a Fair Pensions Guide UK (FPG UK) and would build on the  annual benchmarking studies that ShareAction conducts of institutional investors and represent an extension of the FFG.
The FPG UK will expand the FFGI both into the UK and into the scrutiny of pension providers.  It will do so in the framework of FFGI partners across the different countries collaborating on developing a methodology to assess the performance of pension providers and allow for comparison across geographies.</narrative>
  </description>
